  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Spa Ashoka </strong></p>
<p>For those wishing to truly relax you can enjoy the Ashoka spa where you can enjoy a relaxation area, sauna, steam bath and infra-red sauna or enjoy treatments (bookable and payable locally).</p>
<p><strong>Manta Diving Madeira </strong></p>
<p>On site at the hotel you'll find Manta Diving Madeira where those wishing to discover the underwater nature reserve can take part in diving (bookable and payable locally).</p>
<p><strong>Additional hotel facilities:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Outdoor swimming pool</li>
<li>Indoor swimming pool (located at the neighbouring Hotel Sentido Galosol)</li>
<li>Sun terrace</li>
<li>Garden</li>
<li>Lounge area</li>
<li>Fitness area (located at the neighbouring Hotel Sentido Galosol)</li>
<li>Squash courts (payable locally)</li>
<li>Yoga (subject to hotel schedule, bookable and payable locally)</li>
</ul>]]></facilityDescription>
